abstract: Phillip Alder Bridge column on deal played at District 3 Winter Regional in Rye Brook, NY.
lead_paragraph: Alison Wilson, Chris Willenken, Bjorn Fallenius and Andrew Rosenthal of New York City won the Open Swiss Teams on Jan. 17 at the District 3 Winter Regional.
